# App Database tree

sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant CLI as "InventoryManagerCLI (main)"
    participant Loader as "load_sheet()"
    participant Finder as "find_low_stock()"
    participant Printer as "_print_alerts()"
    User->>CLI: Run CLI with file path and options
    CLI->>Loader: load_sheet(file)
    Loader-->>CLI: DataFrame
    CLI->>Finder: find_low_stock(DataFrame, quantity_col, reorder_col)
    Finder-->>CLI: Low-stock DataFrame
    CLI->>Printer: _print_alerts(Low-stock DataFrame, quantity_col, reorder_col)
    Printer-->>CLI: Print alerts
    CLI-->>User: Exit code
